title: Falafel Al Hana
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Fast food, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available.  Formerly all veg, but now offer meat as well. Specialty is their recipe for falafel. Features small or large falafel pita sandwiches, self-service salad and toppings bar. Approximately £3.20 for a small sandwich to £4.80 for a large sandwich with aubergine & humus.
